---
title: Mediterranean-Style Baked Barramundi with Herby Chickpea Couscous
description: Grab an 8x8-inch baking dish for this Mediterranean inspired bake. Chickpeas, tomatoes and zucchini roast while barramundi cooks on top. It's all served over fluffy couscous for a quick and easy meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-style-baked-barramundi-34ef26f9.jpg
